["ALICE", "bob", "ChArLiE", null] >> names.

"--- Normalizing Case ---" >> Display.

names >> Map:
    @ >> item.
    item >> Type >> check:
        is "list": "" >> Return.
    ..
    item >> Uppercase >> Return.
.. >> normalized_names.

"Normalized: " >> msg.
(normalized_names >> ToJson) >+> msg.
msg >> Display.
